<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#sidllway">不堪[bùkān]</a></strong><strong>2. <a href="#bmobhezv">不堪[bùkān]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="#sidllway">不堪[bùkān]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[be not qualified]∶不能胜任,不能承当</p><p>不堪此重任</p></li><li><p>[how can I bear to]∶忍受不了</p><p>不堪母驱使。--《玉台新咏.古诗为焦仲卿妻作》</p><p>不堪回首</p><p>不堪其苦</p></li><li><p>[may not;improbable]∶不可能,不可</p><p>不堪入耳</p></li></ol></dd></dl><dl><dt><a name="#bmobhezv">不堪[bùkān]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[utterly;extremely]∶用于形容词后面表示程度深</p><p>忙碌不堪</p><p>疲备不堪</p></li><li><p>[too bad]∶坏到极点</p><p>那饭菜都系不堪之物。--《红楼梦》</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
